/*]]>*/</style></p>
<div class=3D"toc-macro rbtoc1485852669732">=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Setuptheconfiguration-PlatformUIConfigurationfiles">Platfor=
mUI Configuration files</a>=20
<ul class=3D"toc-indentation">=20
<li><a href=3D"#Setuptheconfiguration-JavaScriptmodulesinyui.yml">JavaScrip=
t modules in yui.yml</a></li>=20
<li><a href=3D"#Setuptheconfiguration-CSSfilesincss.yml">CSS files in css.y=
ml</a></li>=20
